tool_description: Get a list of tested free proxies working against a specific target
name: Working Free Proxy List Generator
title: Working Free Proxy List Generator

api_list.name: Get Proxies for Target
api_list.description: Get a list of proxies for a specific target site. All proxies are tested for a successful connection to the target before being returned.

required_parameters.name: target
required_parameters.description: Target site the proxies should be tested against

optional_parameters.name: country
optional_parameters.description: Single value or comma separated list of countries in which you wish the proxies to be located. Default = all

optional_parameters.name: timeout
optional_parameters.description: Maximum acceptable wait time for a response from the proxy sever. Max = 3.0, Default = 3.0

optional_parameters.name: protocol
optional_parameters.description: A single value or comma separated list of the proxy protocols you require. Default = all. Options = socks5, socks4, http
